plyTime":"2021-04-30T09:31:41.000Z","msg":"議員：<br />\nWhy not呀？<br />\n你咁講係因為你懶係受過高等教育<br />\n出入又懶係上流社會<br />\n係你嘅懶係學識認為屎就係無聊同污穢嘅<br />\n<br />\n就等於你老母或者大姨媽<br />\n由細到大就話畀你聽鬼就係恐怖嘅一樣<br />\n所以就算篤屎唔臭你都一樣睇佢唔起<br />\n鬼唔埋嚟咬你你都一樣會驚<br />\n如果我哋反轉到呢個觀念就得啦。"},{"pid":"a6a642b9e79daba641bca7851071aa8baa1a6b3e","tid":2510573,"uid":36058,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:34:12.000Z","msg":"同啲人食中藥一樣"},{"pid":"523a71912bd4fb9dc17c50db387d36ee5a258648","tid":2510573,"uid":103916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"用古代思想，殺現代支那病毒？"},{"pid":"aa98b23954d0c09db06166882546ec92df0d0492","tid":2510573,"uid":194399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36515791c3251081d9e9ac68833f81e9b54b989d","tid":2510573,"uid":321977,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"有咩慘過中武肺？<br />\n就係中完仲要飲尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:36:11.000Z","msg":"不如一槍打死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8be5515f9a7771c1fdef57eda82da80c437b978","tid":2510573,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"36515791c3251081d9e9ac68833f81e9b54b989d","tid":2510573,"uid":321977,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:12:04.000Z","msg":"有咩慘過中武肺？<br />\n就係中完仲要飲尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:39:38.000Z","msg":"仲要係冇反抗能力之下焗住飲"},{"pid":"bc3ae774ac7cd0e869f2c80fd1cf5a832c347c2f","tid":2510573,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T09:41:10.000Z","msg":"有冇人淨係睇標題已經笑到噴水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有既俾個正評黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"